<p id="_14e59dbb-7e9c-40a9-1061-81287dcf9cce">This radiation was endorsed by the CIPM as a secondary representation of the definition of the second <eref type="inline" bibitemid="ci2006" citeas="[2]"/>.</p>
</clause>

